-- Leighton Gets $550 Million of Road, Port Projects in India, Company Says
-- Lisa Pham
-- 2010-06-30T23:38:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-30/leighton-gets-550-million-of-road-port-projects-in-india-company-says.html

          
          
             Leighton Holdings Ltd. reported that
Leighton India has been awarded two infrastructure projects
worth $550 million. The company released the information in a
statement to the Australian stock exchange today.
